---
title: Slow-Cooked Pork & Pumpkin Ramen-Style Noodle Souple Soup with Soft Boiled Egg
description: Do you love ramen as much as we do? How could you not - tender pork and noodles swimming around together in a hot, savoury broth and topped with a perfectly jammy egg. This one’s super easy to make as well, just throw everything in your slow cooker and come back when the aroma is calling out to you!
